Module com.gersonfaneto.yams
Package com.gersonfaneto.yams.models.orders.work

Class WorkOrder

java.lang.Object
com.gersonfaneto.yams.models.orders.work.WorkOrder
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class WorkOrder extends Object implements Serializable
Represents the Work Orders that can be created by the Technicians of the Assistance to group the Services requested by a Client, using the "State" pattern to encapsulate some of its mutable behavior.
Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Gerson Ferreira dos Anjos Neto
